{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Registered keeper to be held responsible for hit & runs if driver not identified",
        "additional_details": "The registered keeper is held responsible for most things including parking tickets,  maintaining the vehicle, insuring and taxing. To avoid unnecessary stress, eliminate blaming and for responsibility to be taken, I believe this will have a significant change so in the event of a hit & run, the registered keeper is held responsible.",
        "background": "We want registered keepers to be held responsible for hit and runs if the driver fails to admit liability.",
